The,BCL,easyPDF,Cloud,API,is,a,simple,platform,for,creating,generating,and,automating,PDF,documents,Users,do,not,require,different,APIs,for,different,file,formats,such,as,Excel,HTML,PowerPoint,Word,and,images,because,the,BCL,easyPDF,Cloud,API,is,a,one,stop,solution,for,all,these,file,formats,The,API,sends,requests,and,returns,responses,in,HTTP,and,JSON,formats,respectively,Its,authorization,requires,Basic,OAuth,and,token,authentication,The,API,s,documentation,is,accompanied,by,client,libraries,and,sample,source,codes